{"tid":858114,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"施政報告：5千億起人工島惹眾怒　網民發起改名大賽","createTime":"2018-10-11T14:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T14:57:17.000Z","uid":141630,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6779f7ce293ed90666c83f7ddc4476f5f7451f2a","tid":858114,"uid":141630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181010/photo/bkn-20181010155157625-1010_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181010171316\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181010%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181010155157625-1010_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181010171316&h=0b50466b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181010/bkn-20181010155157625-1010_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181010%2Fbkn-20181010155157625-1010_00822_001.html&d=WycYc52wu3DUnJ9YT9Mr%2Ff755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=60035397\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181010/bkn-20181010155157625-1010_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n政府有意在大嶼山填海興建1700公頃的人工島，連同基建設施，造價相信「四、五千億港元走唔甩」。消息一出，旋即惹來網民狂鬧，填詞人梁栢堅更在Facebook上發起「人工島命名大賽」，創意名字，令人忍俊不禁。以下是梁和一眾網民的爆笑創作節錄：<br />\n<br />\n-敗家島<br />\n-起唔X島<br />\n-款撥唔島<br />\n-不安全島<br />\n-兵敗嶼山島<br />\n-政府永遠聽唔島<br />\n-也會怕有一天會跌島<br />\n-起到都住唔島（網民JuDy Chan）<br />\n-慘不忍島（網民Bryan Tam）<br />\n-估你唔島（網民Easybet Lau）<br />\n<br />\n其實這些島名，除了能看出網民的幽默，似乎亦反映了一般小市民的無奈。有網民坦言，不明白為何「明明新界咁多地，係要填海造地......」有網民更「係咁食字」，抒發心中怨氣：「起得島也未必好，小島移情，大島亂政，有目共島」。"},{"pid":"0643c6e46cb3bdc1d967f7f349dbb9b5e2fc57a0","tid":858114,"uid":46042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:31:28.000Z","msg":"屌你老島"},{"pid":"c74c6c2825a6ee044b64513864cccb54db931988","tid":858114,"uid":31261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:34:55.000Z","msg":"島錢落海"},{"pid":"d06272c1741003c902bccbb60648780008b12d33","tid":858114,"uid":141711,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:40:01.000Z","msg":"改名有閪用咩"},{"pid":"253a2b6c326141290bdd24c839dd339a3746b430","tid":858114,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:50:14.000Z","msg":"起唔撚島 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑到仆街"},{"pid":"55623c72fe0841146e5620282f12e2052de3208e","tid":858114,"uid":13257,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:53:27.000Z","msg":"惹起眾怒，所以幫個島改名<br />\n<br />\n睇嚟真係好嬲"},{"pid":"c54aee6b1555aa37fdbeff9cedc432204136a216","tid":858114,"uid":39413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"55623c72fe0841146e5620282f12e2052de3208e","tid":858114,"uid":13257,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:53:27.000Z","msg":"惹起眾怒，所以幫個島改名<br />\n<br />\n睇嚟真係好嬲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:55:34.000Z","msg":"嚇撚到啲高官腳軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5020c4913598a3e2d7d34d82a9ea94a86e760ce4","tid":858114,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又真係幾鬧"},{"pid":"02e42c0a6c9342d3c7f8dabf23253a445a0a73e6","tid":858114,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:56:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又真係幾嬲</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c0f98b5b88abd17bb091d9c8f2566cd699a1d26a","tid":858114,"uid":48286,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:57:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: brown;\">認認真真諗下點樣拆掂佢，點樣抗爭啦，做埋啲戇鳩嘢，使唔使加插唱埋卡拉ok，BBQ？<br />\n<br />\n呢班仆街肯撚定係雨傘期間打邊爐嗰班撚樣</span>"}]}